==Installation==

Install into ~kiosk/sodafw:
    make install

(export PATH="$PATH:/home/kiosk/sodafw/bin")

Monitor the Bus
    ctool -monitor somethingthatwontshowup

Kill everything
    sudo -u kiosk cprocman stop

Start everything
    sudo -u kiosk cprocman start

Etc.


==Layout==

+ doc -- *.txt written, the javadoc and perl doc are generated by make docs
+ libs -- libs that the fingerprint server depend upon
+ src -- Our Code
 + fp-server -- Fingerprint Server
 + conf -- Configuration Files
 + lib -- libraries, the io bus, and some of the ui interaction
   + com/theamk/ambus -- java version of the bus
 + mdb-server -- bobdb server
 + misc -- random
 + moz-kiosk -- gtk-embedd interaction-fu
 + scripts -- most of the actual scripts
 + vmc-server -- vending machine server
